:-1,"quote":{"pid":"d2ea9a88625ab062536a8b5f16cce0740a6126ae","tid":1097784,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你嗰陣到咗台灣即刻book?,由book睇醫生至做完手術嗰日用咗幾多日？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:43:00.000Z","msg":"好似去之前兩日先BOOK 佢地日日都有唔同醫生係度<br />\n同埋呢科無乜人睇 因為要自費 台灣人唔會想比錢睇醫生<br />\n呢科會做埋割雙眼皮果類野 我打左長途去問 佢拎我護照號碼幫我BOOK<br />\n佢會講你知幾時睇 到果日可以仲上網睇返睇到你未 不過佢都會講定時間比你 話幾點睇第幾個 你早去會比你睇完<br />\n我唔記得早幾耐BOOK 都係早幾日先打 原本諗住WALK IN<br />\n我到台灣第二日睇 睇完個醫生就話可以即做 等佢睇埋兩三個病人<br />\n睇完就換袍簽紙<br />\n坐左陣就入手術室<br />\n你可以打去問一問先 佢會問你想搵邊個醫生 你話求其得啦 割粉瘤<br />\n佢會幫你諗搵邊個會好D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我有朋友住台灣，諗住睇下佢可唔可以幫我book，等我去到台灣第一日有得做。<br />\n<br />\nBtw巴打粒粉瘤幾大？我粉瘤大概1毫子左右，凸咗0.3-0.4cm出嚟，好核突，個手術應該係成個囊袋割出嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T23:27:13.000Z","msg":"唔好打台大醫院個人工掛號 直接打去果科<br />\n我果粒好似幾大 係耳後 夾住成日發炎<br />\n我唔係幾記得 總之大過你 <br />\n係呀 其實5分鐘就夾左出黎<br />\n係縫針耐d 半粒鐘啦成個過程 完全無乜feel<br />\n佢都話好大機會復發 幫我割乾淨d 機會會低d"},{"pid":"0f9466a0a9981082cd40f1933388c80271c2ee7c","tid":1097784,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2c05eb21b395a21efcf4b63fdc7167605e8844c","tid":1097784,"uid":235021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"03d3f7aa2397da17b16729255512e22988fb1ad2","tid":1097784,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0f1414c623ae9c55441396824eb22f6a1607390","tid":1097784,"uid":235021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:45:04.000Z","msg":"之前係中環私家割$5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:13:35.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記錯，原來只係放濃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T08:11:14.000Z","msg":"放濃自己放都得啦 <br />\n我成日自己篤穿佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過幾個月d 濃又積埋"},{"pid":"5650c556b30515995d17d779e76b0d85098c1c1d","tid":1097784,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"555b888335ee110c398777f478652ba0863e28c7","tid":1097784,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5cc3fc4e61c10aace853a92a889edc7e9d5eede","tid":1097784,"uid":123082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T15:55:05.000Z","msg":"排左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年做<br />\n<br />\n好似比左2百幾，一部分係住院費（即日出院）同洗傷口<br />\n<br />\n但近排又生返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪手勢差定佢冇成個囊割出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我睇醫生個時腫到成個半粒波子咁大<br />\n<br />\n幾個月後爆左<br />\n<br />\n跟著兩年後終於等到做手術個日，但係個時冇腫<br />\n<br />\n咁我就指返個啲位（係耳背黎 我睇唔到 淨係指比佢睇）<br />\n<br />\n跟著佢話 哦～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用maker圈起左就入手術室<br />\n<br />\n之前一直都對做手術冇乜feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但上床個刻先有驚既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n我都唔知係米成個囊割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc666753fc3696b2832052344554383092985c9","tid":1097784,"uid":13095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc54d421466e1548a1b8cb12e81e146c5db1e3b","tid":109